How to Unmask a Lie
A look at the current headlines shows how questionable and widespread deception and lies are in daily life.
Republican presidential candidate Herman Cain is busy trying to deal with the allegations of sexual harassment on the part of several women. Both sides accuse each other of lying.
Penn State's leadership is accused of perjury, as one has allegedly withheld reports that a retired football coach sexually assaulted boys.
