The homeowners had 11 of the 13 apartments in the building on Balmes Street No. 51 (Barcelona) occupied.
The twelve squatters left the building yesterday afternoon without resisting.
Everything points to the fact that the nightmares of the neighbors of the house No. 51 have come to an end on the street Balmes.
Twelve people voluntarily left the building yesterday at noon, which they illegally occupied and in which they had organized huge festivals that had driven the neighborhood to despair. The eviction was made by court order without police intervention.
